        <main class="page-main">
            <div class="page-wrap">
                <section class="card compose" id="create-post">
                    <div class="compose-row">
                        <img id="home-current-user-avatar" class="avatar avatar-md" src="" alt="Current user avatar">
                        <div class="grow">
                            <textarea class="textarea" placeholder="Ban dang nghi gi, hom nay?"></textarea>
                            <div class="compose-footer">
                                <div class="muted small">
                                    Dang dang nhap voi <span id="home-current-user-name">Account</span>
                                </div>
                                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button">Dang bai</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <div class="posts-list">
                    <article class="card post-card">
                        <div class="post-header">
                            <div class="author-row">
                                <img class="avatar avatar-md" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=150&h=150&fit=crop" alt="Tran Thi B">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="author-name">Tran Thi B</p>
                                    <p class="author-meta">@@tranthib · 2 ngay truoc</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-content">Vua hoan thanh du an thiet ke app mobile cho mon UI/UX. Rat tu hao voi ket qua hien tai. Moi nguoi cho minh xin them feedback nhe.</div>
                        <div class="post-actions">
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn active" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m12 21-1.35-1.23C5.4 15 2 11.91 2 8.14 2 5.06 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.06 22 8.14c0 3.77-3.4 6.86-8.65 11.63L12 21Z"></path></svg></span><span>45</span></button>
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></span><span>2</span></button>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card post-card">
                        <div class="post-header">
                            <div class="author-row">
                                <img class="avatar avatar-md" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599566150163-29194dcaad36?w=150&h=150&fit=crop" alt="Le Quang C">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="author-name">Le Quang C</p>
                                    <p class="author-meta">@@lequangc · 2 ngay truoc</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-content">Chia se mot so tips hoc ReactJS hieu qua: practice moi ngay, build project that, doc documentation va tham gia community.</div>
                        <div class="post-actions">
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn active" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m12 21-1.35-1.23C5.4 15 2 11.91 2 8.14 2 5.06 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.06 22 8.14c0 3.77-3.4 6.86-8.65 11.63L12 21Z"></path></svg></span><span>78</span></button>
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></span><span>1</span></button>
                        </div>
