                    <article class="card post-card">
                        <div class="post-header">
                            <div class="author-row">
                                <img class="avatar avatar-md" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=150&h=150&fit=crop" alt="Pham Thi D">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="author-name">Pham Thi D</p>
                                    <p class="author-meta">@@phamthid · 2 ngay truoc</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-content">Hom nay duoc tham gia workshop ve Machine Learning tai FPT. Rất nhieu kien thuc moi va thu vi.</div>
                        <div class="post-actions">
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn active" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m12 21-1.35-1.23C5.4 15 2 11.91 2 8.14 2 5.06 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.06 22 8.14c0 3.77-3.4 6.86-8.65 11.63L12 21Z"></path></svg></span><span>56</span></button>
                            <button class="subtle-btn action-btn" type="button"><span class="icon icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></span><span>0</span></button>
                        </div>
                    </article>
